	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Safehouse Interview: City of Heroes Arist, Chris Chamblerlain.</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Freonsmurf</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Jun 24, 2004, 17:07</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Safehouse%20Interview%3A%20City%20of%20Heroes%20Arist%2C%20Chris%20Chamblerlain.&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Finterviews%2Farticle_20.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
